{"tid":2207773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[長文] 見到班ON9喺度屌小店偽黃，原來黃店門檻咁撚高","createTime":"2020-09-18T11:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T17:00:19.000Z","uid":351252,"like":28,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"44e7627fe92809bb2e824cc7c4b53dfd99394033","tid":2207773,"uid":351252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T11:24:13.000Z","msg":"日撚日入到個facebook group啲人都食嗰幾間<br />\n只要有人話邊間唔好食、貴、衛生差就俾人屌到上天花板<br />\n你老味，開餐廳最基本要求就係味道唔差、夠衛生，<br />\n幾時黃店就可以豁免？如果係咁咪撚開餐廳，做第啲生意可能好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n琴日有個member開post介紹新開餐廳，講明未知顏色，<br />\n成班撚樣又jer撚住佢話唔知顏色就唔好post啦冇興趣知<br />\n有ON9無憑無據就話人打手廣告<br />\n更加有人癡撚線到代樓主whatsapp舖頭問人黃定藍<br />\n底下留言仲好似expect人哋真係24小時standby<br />\n未覆就話即係綠啦、綠即係藍啦又乜又柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好喇人哋終於回覆咗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CtfnNhO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCtfnNhO.jpg&h=4093c0d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喂屌你我以為去到呢度應該收聲啦<br />\n咪撚再jer樓主<br />\n點撚知更加cls嘅撚樣真係出現咗<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i58QbNc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi58QbNc.jpg&h=5b507313&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FkzS9yT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFkzS9yT.jpg&h=33549e92&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/njyMuyT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnjyMuyT.jpg&h=1f67fbea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nWTF???? up mud 9???<br />\n原來要俾人扑頭搞鳩間舖先真黃???<br />\n仲話唔係想鬥黃<br />\n咁唔叫鬥黃叫乜嘢<br />\n黨安法之前黃店老細都俾人扑穿頭<br />\n而家你想人點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人哋答你已經好撚俾面你班撚樣<br />\n答咗又唔撚滿意話藍絲都識講好撚鍾意香港<br />\n咁我夠話你淨係講句光復香港時代革命都係偽黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人哋做過啲乜洗唔洗話你知?<br />\n你班撚樣知道咗慌死唔會唱通街害撚到人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以俾返少少sense唔好咁ON9<br />\n圍錯人柒咗仲要柒多幾錢重<br />\n有理性嘅人出聲就藍絲五毛分化<br />\n佢班撚樣亂話人就係革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日撚日喺度chur自己友真心唔知做乜鳩<br />\n而家係黃都有成本<br />\n班撚樣話人扮<br />\n扮黃唔撚洗成本嘅?<br />\n班撚樣圍爐亂屌人鬥黃9UP就真係唔洗成本喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成撚日話淨係食返已知嘅黃店<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">仲好意思話壯大黃色經圈</span></span><br />\n日撚日淨係食嗰啲咪得囉<br />\n而家多一個隊友都唔撚滿意<br />\njer撚住人，答咗你班撚樣又話咁樣都唔黃<br />\n<br />\n咁搞法根本唔洗對家出手<br />\n班撚樣鬥死自己人先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPOST LINK:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/tuenyuentin/?multi_permalinks=701849650431757&amp;comment_id=702515390365183&amp;notif_id=1600325926041028&amp;notif_t=feedback_reaction_generic&amp;ref=notif\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Ftuenyuentin%2F%3Fmulti_permalinks%3D701849650431757%26comment_id%3D702515390365183%26notif_id%3D1600325926041028%26notif_t%3Dfeedback_reaction_generic%26ref%3Dnotif&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdcRCHeky4xD%2FQbA%2BfbsvJuc%3D&h=a73d44fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/tuenyuentin/?multi_permalinks=701849650431757&amp;comment_id=702515390365183&amp;notif_id=1600325926041028&amp;notif_t=feedback_reaction_generic&amp;ref=notif</a>"},{"pid":"ce59b9f4ed949d12ffe0a7c1e5cc9e596b137dca","tid":2207773,"uid":118127,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"re